SQL is used to communicate with a database. it includes Database Creation, Database Deletion, Fetching Data Rows, Modifying & Deleting Data.
Queries-
SELECT * FROM EMP;
SELECT ENAME, HIREDATE FROM EMP;
SELECT EMANE,DEPTNO,JOB FROM EMP WHERE JOB='CLERK';
SELECT SAL, SAL*12, SAL*6 FROM EMP;
SELECT * FROM DEPT;
SELECT DISTINCT JOB,SAL FROM EMP;
SELECT JOB FROM EMP;
SELECT LOC FROM DEPT;

